title: John Oliver's 'Stand Your Ground' Lies DEBUNKED!
description: John Oliver had a lot of stupid things to say about “Stand Your Ground” laws. We pick them apart one by one. Pope Tony Fauci had his biggest COVID flip-flop to date, and this one proves Donald Trump RIGHT! Also, another example of how Gretchen Whitmer is a horrible governor who sucks at life.
